.Sh CAVEATS
One instance of
.Nm ,
and therefore one local port,
is required for each server connection.
.
.Pp
The
.Nm
daemon makes no distinction between channels.
Elevated activity in one channel
may push messages from a quieter channel
out of the buffer.
.
